    "description": "<p>Established in 2015, Salling Search is a leading search and recruitment consultancy headquartered in Singapore with a branch office in Denmark.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Our specialisation lies in sourcing exceptional mid to senior-level talent within the Maritime, Trading and Logistics sectors worldwide.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Aspiring to be the best choice for both candidates and clients, we offer bespoke recruitment solutions tailored to their unique needs. With a global reach, we excel in identifying and attracting top maritime talent to drive success worldwide.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Salling Search Pte Ltd (EA License No: 15S7671)<br>\nwww.sallingsearch.com</p>",
